story.storykicker: The West Bengal Joint Entrance Examination results, WBJEE to be declared today, June 5 at www.wbjeeb.nic.in.
story.storybody:
The West Bengal Joint Entrance Examination (WBJEE) results is to be declared today, June 5 at 1:30 pm on www.wbjeeeb.nic.in

The students who are likely to take admission in different professional courses like Engineering/ Architecture can know their results after 1:30, the official time for declaration of result as per board.

The joint entrance exam result was held this year on May 17 in various examination centers of the state

Steps to know the result:

  • Log on to www.wbjeeb.nic.in
  • Enter your roll number
  • Result will appear on the screen
  • Save the result and take a print out for future reference.

About the Board

The West Bengal joint Entrance Examinations Board was established in the year 1962 and its basic purpose is to conduct engineering and medical entrance examination in the state.
